this (consistent with notifications payload format):
```js
{
    "data": [
        {
            "bucket_id": "2f9b1aaa-552d-48e8-1b78-371dd08688b3", 
            "collection_id": "test", 
            "permissions": [
                "write", 
                "read", 
                "record:create"
            ], 
            "resource_name": "collection", 
